div1.ab: Territory of Washington County of King SS
div1.p: I do hereby return to the Hon. Roger S. Greene Chief Justice of Washington Territory, and Judge of the Third Judicial District, that before the coming to the of his alledged writ. The said James Carpenter was committed to my custody, and is contained by virtue of another writ, a copy of which is herewith annexed; no original of which, I also herewith produce; nevertheless, I have the body of the said James Carpenter, before you at the time ady and place within mentioned, as I am within commanded
